pageContext.claim: “We have done an incredible job. Throughout the world, I get called by prime ministers and presidents saying, ‘Sir, the job you've done is amazing.’”
pageContext.analysis: Highly dubious. The use of "sir" is often a tell that this is an invented conversation. The U.S. has not contained the coronavirus as well as many peer nations. The country leads in total deaths and ranks high in deaths per 100,000 people.
